Fans of the series will find a very bite-sized example of the open-ended gameplay coming in The Phantom Pain. You can bet there will be a huge map with several bases like this for Snake to infiltrate at his leisure.", "timestamp_created": 1426134461, "timestamp_updated": 1426134461, "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "weighted_vote_score": 0.5, "comment_count": 0, "steam_purchase": false, "received_for_free": false, "written_during_early_access": false, "primarily_steam_deck": false}

