{"recommendationid": "14521429", "author": {"steamid": "76561197998204301", "num_games_owned": 0, "num_reviews": 27, "playtime_forever": 1107, "playtime_last_two_weeks": 0, "playtime_at_review": 562, "last_played": 1441460378}, "language": "english", "review": "Favourite series of all time by my favourite developer. I am so grateful to them for releasing on PC. If they didn't, I would have to buy a PS4 for literally just two games; this and Phantom Pain.

