Very excited for MGS5, I only wish Kojima would release the Metal Gear Collection on Steam, I'd buy it in a heartbeat!", "timestamp_created": 1422262502, "timestamp_updated": 1422262502, "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 1, "votes_funny": 0, "weighted_vote_score": "0.502262473106384277", "comment_count": 0, "steam_purchase": true, "received_for_free": false, "written_during_early_access": false, "primarily_steam_deck": false}

{"recommendationid": "14123621", "author": {"steamid": "76561198150998545", "num_games_owned": 0, "num_reviews": 26, "playtime_forever": 2852, "playtime_last_two_weeks": 0, "playtime_at_review": 1249, "last_played": 1440696096}, "language": "english", "review": "Too bad it wasn't part of The Phantom Pain (which Kojima would've wanted it that way. More emotional booms), but blame Konami for making it so.

Anyway, it's a great shift to open-world stealth with guns. Really widening the MGS world to a whole new level, adding more options to what you want to do and how you want to clear your missions. Story is linear, but there are minor details added in which might shift a bit in your playthrough.

Also, it sucks that the console players had to pay 60 bucks for this. Glad we have it 20, huh?", "timestamp_created": 1422006827, "timestamp_updated": 1422006827, "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 2, "votes_funny": 1, "weighted_vote_score": "0.475030571222305298", "comment_count": 0, "steam_purchase": true, "received_for_free": false, "written_during_early_access": false, "primarily_steam_deck": false}

