Worth the money all day, would buy again without hesitation.", "timestamp_created": 1421875280, "timestamp_updated": 1421875280, "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "weighted_vote_score": 0.5, "comment_count": 0, "steam_purchase": true, "received_for_free": false, "written_during_early_access": false, "primarily_steam_deck": false}

{"recommendationid": "14073213", "author": {"steamid": "76561197967954785", "num_games_owned": 0, "num_reviews": 15, "playtime_forever": 283, "playtime_last_two_weeks": 0, "playtime_at_review": 12, "last_played": 1618706358}, "language": "english", "review": "An amazing game, but Keifer Sutherland's voice ruins Snake.  Makes me wish for Japanese audio, so I don't have to listen to him.

