{"recommendationid": "13657248", "author": {"steamid": "76561198025442218", "num_games_owned": 643, "num_reviews": 32, "playtime_forever": 319, "playtime_last_two_weeks": 0, "playtime_at_review": 319, "last_played": 1419747576}, "language": "english", "review": "A demo for MGS 5 : Phantom Pain, buy it if you want extra acheivements, or need to test Phantom Pain's engine on your hardware before forking out the real moneys ( https://store.steampowered.com/app/287700/METAL_GEAR_SOLID_V_THE_PHANTOM_PAIN/ ).  Once again, Solid Snake is nowhere to be found, so the series name is a misnomer.  There are a couple of extra "replay value" modes, and the usual in-game cutscenes that last faaar too long.  But hey, they are a hallmark, right?

