{"recommendationid": "13473753", "author": {"steamid": "76561197966547181", "num_games_owned": 0, "num_reviews": 54, "playtime_forever": 1985, "playtime_last_two_weeks": 0, "playtime_at_review": 584, "last_played": 1683168210}, "language": "english", "review": "Having already played and beaten the game many times on PS4, I knew what I was getting when I bought this game on Steam.  While short if taken at face value, there's TONS of stuff here to keep you busy for hours and hours.  Tapes, Badges, missions and lots of other hidden secrets including the 2 console DLC missions.  Just learning to play the game and find different ways and methods of infiltrating Camp Omega provides lots of fun and entertainment.  If you are the type of gamer that likes to replay missions and try to beat your previous records, then this game will suit your interests well.

