{"recommendationid": "13453721", "author": {"steamid": "76561197993440921", "num_games_owned": 1418, "num_reviews": 139, "playtime_forever": 895, "playtime_last_two_weeks": 0, "playtime_at_review": 525, "last_played": 1419366254}, "language": "english", "review": "An absolutely incredible experience for an incredible price. There's no doubt that most people will feel shunned at the fact that this is a prologue to the main game "The Phantom Pain", but I think it's well worth the money. 

