{"recommendationid": "13453580", "author": {"steamid": "76561198019117919", "num_games_owned": 3854, "num_reviews": 22, "playtime_forever": 1015, "playtime_last_two_weeks": 0, "playtime_at_review": 484, "last_played": 1441060033}, "language": "english", "review": "I'm pleasantly surprised to find that there is much more content here than what the internet has been claiming since it's release. $30 is certainly too much for it, but the price now is more than fair for what you get.

