{"recommendationid": "13451154", "author": {"steamid": "76561197997681451", "num_games_owned": 1653, "num_reviews": 177, "playtime_forever": 1867, "playtime_last_two_weeks": 0, "playtime_at_review": 1317, "last_played": 1440962327}, "language": "english", "review": "Amazingly optimized PC version, there's a few control gripes with mouse and keyboard and I wish there were more Anti-Aliasing options, and worst of all you can't import your own music onto your helicopter like you can with the PS3 and PS4 versions (That's such a fucking bummer, seriously) but that is the extent of my complaints with the port. I'm so glad I waited out this PC version instead of buying it for my PS3.

